com.mercadopago.resources

Class MerchantOrder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mercadopago.core.MPBase
      • com.mercadopago.resources.MerchantOrder

  • public class MerchantOrder
extends MPBase
    This class will allow you to create and manage your orders. You can attach one or more payments in your merchant order.
